This routine fills a rectangular output area from a single column of N values using column-major ordering.

**Python:**
```python
def column_major_transpose(values, R, C, ws, start_row, start_col):
    for i, value in enumerate(values):
        row = start_row + (i % R)
        col = start_col + (i // R)
        ws.cell(row=row, column=col, value=value)
